name: SIKZONOATE #2
description:
This is a series of mine which include 4 pieces of my personal paintings during the phase of my therapy in 2018.
The name of this series is actually the name of the injection that I had several times everyday for two years.

The 4 paintings represent things that I hallucinated and dreamt about back then.

All paintings are acrylic on paper but I sell the digital version only.
Enjoy.
